Massachusetts COVID-19 Analysis

This page displays analysis of Massachusetts COVID-19 data from the Massachusetts Department of Public Health (MDPH) and the Massachusetts Wastewater Resources Authority (MWRA).

Daily statistics from MDPH

The charts below display daily data compiled by MDPH on COVID-19 cases, hospitalizations, and deaths in Massachusetts. The most recent data is through 2022-06-04.

Wastewater Analysis

The charts below display data collected by the Massachusetts Wastewater Resources Authority (MWRA) on levels of COVID-19 in Boston-area wastewater. For more information, see the MWRA site.
